{"tid":1512862,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"奇女子闖楊屋道攔截九巴　角鐵扑爆車門被捕","createTime":"2019-08-28T05:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T15:25:06.000Z","uid":7439,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"89e35eb9709b39950cb9a5784cd18bb0d0af75bf","tid":1512862,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:18:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210388/org/3ff0342fd168619afdddde6472c452c4.jpg/vZBCdhiMqd_hMyuJLXU1ymQO4kf3yfDi4zKsY8kyrGM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210388%2Forg%2F3ff0342fd168619afdddde6472c452c4.jpg%2FvZBCdhiMqd_hMyuJLXU1ymQO4kf3yfDi4zKsY8kyrGM&h=f41f8cd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190828/photo/bkn-20190828061909327-0828_00822_001_02b.jpg?20190828073950\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190828%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190828061909327-0828_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20190828073950&h=18fa4afb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荃灣發生刑事毀壞案。今日(28日)清晨5時56分，一部行走42A路線的九巴，由車廠駛往長亨邨投入服務，當駛經楊屋道45號街市對開，一名女子從行人路上跑出馬路攔截巴士，並取出一條角鐵扑毀巴士的前門，巴士車長報警，女子破壞後並沒有逃走。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190828/_2019082808391064364.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190828%2F_2019082808391064364.jpg&h=451d336b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方到場調查時，該名28歲女子疑精神有異，並聲稱自己為內地人，但不能出示身份證明文件。警方經調查後，以涉嫌刑事毀壞及不能出示證件將她拘捕，她由救護員送院治理。案件交由荃灣警區刑事調查隊跟進，正調查事件原因。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3210384/org/b8998ec999e01be2463a97bca24ef3d0.jpg/HFsGQlGnosWRNx_vLKAnDs1M1q7_0O79rRel0IcXpdA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3210384%2Forg%2Fb8998ec999e01be2463a97bca24ef3d0.jpg%2FHFsGQlGnosWRNx_vLKAnDs1M1q7_0O79rRel0IcXpdA&h=9bb2338e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0deab6e461f0fa791bd824d5bc6705006048a59","tid":1512862,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:18:22.000Z","msg":"專營公共巴士業務<br />\n九龍巴士（一九三三）有限公司（「九巴」）<br />\n 九巴於 2019 年上半年錄得除稅後盈利港幣 1.677 億 元<br />\n（ 2018 年上半年為港幣 1.925 億元），較 2018 年同期減少<br />\n港 幣 2,480 萬元或 12.9% 。"},{"pid":"d11cb7bf4fe796c6f1c28d7c4bd6c002f3975029","tid":1512862,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=f4820e09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=9d825ba5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=6a82b660\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"494f6865fe1bcddea91f7b692e6bcea7d3a73772","tid":1512862,"uid":229385,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:19:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/powa9ij.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpowa9ij.gif&h=1b058a43&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1419d6dea68bc8acc3b0c06e65338e01e0b017d9","tid":1512862,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T05:22:04.000Z","msg":"大陸西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"